node.text:
Sharing my thoughts after trying out the XP-Pen's Innovator 16 for 3 months!! Overall I'm so glad that this was my first graphic display tablet because it made me understand why people invest in them instead of cheaper tablets, with its highly responsive screen, low power consumption, and smart and sleek design. 

Those of you who have been following my IG stories would know that I've been suffering from art block for months, which frankly made me worried if I could draw for this review....but you'll be able to see from the Draw With Me part of the video how its ergonomic design really helped me maintain my focus to break through the horrid block like it was nothing???!

If this got you interested in the Innovator 16 too, here's your chance because XP-Pen wants to share the joy with one of you with a 🔊 GIVEAWAY 🔊!! (Go visit the giveaway post for instructions to participate!) 

Also if you're looking to purchase the Innovator 16, it is currently 20% off with Mother's Day sales until 18 May!!!! Act fast and save more than 100USD!

US store: https://bit.ly/3vyOzCy
CA store: https://bit.ly/3tgj1A2
(Also linked in my bio for your convenience)

#sponsoredpost #innovator16 #xppen

node.text:
LOL so last night’s comic gave me lots of feelings and i channeled them into making a kagehina playlist! kinda tried to structure it in the order of realisation of feelings > pining > angst/hurt > finding their way back to each other > healing > intimacy!

it’s not a complete playlist and i’ll keep editing in the future but if you have any song recs that u think rly fit kagehina lmk and i might add them in (esp if u have suggestions for intimacy segment at the end 🥴) also lmk if you enjoyed listening to it 🥺💕 

it’s monday tomorrow so i will also be listening to it and crying during work from OTP feels lol

linked my spotify profile in bio!

tattoo artists AU - dragon and dragon slayer 🐉 

🌟 this is a modern AU so beidou is reincarnated and crosses paths with rex lapis again

🌟 they both work as tattoo artists and zhongli knows beidou so he knows all the vision holders from liyue and what would resonate with them, that’s why beidou loves her #haishan tattoos that he chose for her a lot but doesn’t know the reason why

🌟will other liyue characters make an appearance? 👁👁 what and where is zhongdong's mysterious tatt?

#beidou #zhongli #genshinimpact #genshinimpactfanart #modernau
